01:23:19,440 --> 01:23:21,360
This is the place.

782
01:23:21,480 --> 01:23:23,840
Where you slayed Grendel's mother.

783
01:23:27,680 --> 01:23:30,360
Wiglaf, I have no sons,

784
01:23:31,320 --> 01:23:35,560
and if this demon kills me,
I have arranged with the heralds

785
01:23:35,640 --> 01:23:36,920
that you shall be king.

