788
01:23:46,200 --> 01:23:48,880
Nay! There is nothing I should know.

789
01:23:49,000 --> 01:23:52,040
You are Beowulf.
Beowulf the mighty, the hero!

790
01:23:52,240 --> 01:23:54,560
The slayer and destroyer of demons!

791
01:23:54,720 --> 01:23:57,040
Now, let us kill this flying devil
where it sleeps

792
01:23:57,120 --> 01:23:59,360
and get on with our bloody lives!

793
01:24:04,520 --> 01:24:07,000
- Do you want me to go in with you?
- No.

794
01:24:08,840 --> 01:24:10,080
Good.

795
01:24:54,680 --> 01:24:56,040
Beowulf.

